    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. This specimen features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle has undergone proactive VANOS bulletproofing and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the high-revving platform. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the tactile feedback and lateral grip expected of the M-division. Finished in original factory paint with a flawless Nappa leather interior, this garaged example shows no signs of thermal cycling or interior bolster wear. A mechanically pristine, turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
