    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car appears as if it just rolled off the showroom floor, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero imperfections\u2014no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple, unscuffed leather that still retains its original factory scent, complemented by high-gloss trim and carpets that have been protected by premium floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature and luxury amenity functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history and has been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a meticulous driver to own a vehicle that has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy. Smoke-free, pet-free, and absolutely turn-key.",
